FbxExportCompatibility: This will set the fbx sdk compatibility when exporting to fbx file. The default value is 2013
bForceFrontXAxis: Convert the scene from FBX coordinate system to UE coordinate system with front X axis instead of -Y
bExportOnlySelectedControls: Whether or not import onto selected controls or all controls
ControlChannelMappings: Mappings for how Control Rig Control Attributes Map to the incoming Transforms
bASCII: If enabled, save as ascii instead of binary
bExportLocalTime: If enabled, export sequencer animation in its local time, relative to its sequence.

methods.name: LoadControlMappingsFromPreset
methods.doc: Load the default or metahuman preset into the current mappings
